>\n最好效果配日本珍珠米，先煮到一粒一粒，煙煙韌韌<br />\n好貴$90 2KG  唔捨得成日食要省住食<br />\n我係有錢買煲冇錢買米<br />\n<br />\n普通珍珠米效果只係一半一半<br />\n平時D 泰國／大陸米只係好少少  分別唔大<br />\n台灣米未試過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有丫媽投訴冇得蒸野 煮飯要另外入水 仲要多左野要拆出尼洗</blockquote><br />\n甘你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甘尼你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊尼甘你老母"},{"pid":"6a704653c2b0103ef430e8e8757a0eb91a8b4086","tid":247130,"uid":82175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"白金離子風筒<br />\n納米水過濾<br />\n水晶磁場<br />\n一國兩制<br />\n港豬橋<br />\n膏鐵"},{"pid":"3eb9f51bf8eea2e7caea2c132fad8ea221488adc","tid":247130,"uid":6643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"好老實<br />\n東芝平過佢 技術唔同<br />\n但食出嚟 好食好多 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg&h=cb11497c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1af5e2e396aa11745ad06217e3f0ff9b40ec1ccf","tid":247130,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:51:36.000Z","msg":"上年母親節夾份送左個比老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚重，<br />\n拎到返屋企先發覺好撚大舊，<br />\n我地呢啲不孝子真係太少入廚房幫阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n煮一煲飯零舍耐，<br />\n屌要48分鐘，快煮都3X，<br />\n快煮仲要煲出黎同普通煲差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓上講得啱，<br />\n佢個效果真係要用日本米先明顯，<br />\n我有朋友開日本餐廳，佢之前有一直幫我地叫米，<br />\n但係次次過去拎又麻煩人，<br />\n搞搞下都係樓下順手買金象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我阿媽原來仲收埋個舊飯煲，<br />\n有時佢同阿仔兩個食，拎出黎蒸埋肉餅又煲飯真係好撚方便嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc3d178d1994d7fce7cb61a68185f9d009bd926","tid":247130,"uid":57304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:52:05.000Z","msg":"我個電飯煲係日本東芝既旗艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本造，個 model 係香港買唔到<br />\n計番買埋個足料唔會打爛野既變壓器都仲平過香港旗艦電飯煲<br />\n結論係好食過普通飯煲既飯，珍珠米更明顯<br />\n<br />\n利申: 買完之後要節衣縮食兩三個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e5ad91589dcdcd5183023b554f3b3593c71312","tid":247130,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實<br />\n東芝平過佢 技術唔同<br />\n但食出嚟 好食好多 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg&h=cb11497c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻都有朋友同我講過，<br />\n不過柒左一次唔敢博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重唔重，大唔大舊？"},{"pid":"90d5f66b615efb1716db0e7c46c5df934bff08a0","tid":247130,"uid":61582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實<br />\n東芝平過佢 技術唔同<br />\n但食出嚟 好食好多 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F094154_52b3d6a54fa73b06cda0aa0f5a7288c8.jpg&h=cb11497c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪5千蚊一個 屋企有個差唔多樣既"},{"pid":"ae4145ff1e3af599427d845b917710f728ec1db8","tid":247130,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28ce0cfc3ff07274654bc48bf1957f4f52f1eca4","tid":247130,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"屋企個個3000幾唔覺有咩特別"},{"pid":"541e8c321516bc8f206beb00b229a7b2772d5b2b","tid":247130,"uid":